Package VendingModel.VendingMachineClasses

Class VendingMachine

java.lang.Object
VendingModel.VendingMachineClasses.VendingMachine
Direct Known Subclasses:
RegularVendingMachine, SpecialVendingMachine
public abstract class VendingMachine extends Object
This is an abstract class for the VendingMachine. It serves as a template for both the Regular and Special Vending Machine. It contains the consatants for the total aount of Items, Denominations, Row, and Collumn. It also contains counting attributes for the different arrays. It has two arrays of Money for user and the machine itself, an ArrayList of Transactions, and a 2 dimensional array for the ItemsSlots.
